        A_CUMBROUS_SILENCE_DESCENDS_AS_THE_ECHOES_OF                          = 11426,  -- A cumbrous silence descends as the echoes of that mysterious internal voice fade away.
        MY_NAME_IS_SVERDHRIED_JOURNEYMAN_AND_PROSELYTIZER_OF                  = 11427,  -- My name is Sverdhried, journeyman and proselytizer of the runic arts.
        MY_NAME_IS_SVERDHRIED_AND_I_LEAVE_THIS                                = 11428,  -- My name is Sverdhried, and I leave this record with little hope of it ever reaching the ears of another.
        I_DISCOVERED_THIS_PARTICULAR_RUNIC_CONTRIVANCE_AFTER_DESCENDING       = 11429,  -- I discovered this particular runic contrivance after descending deep below a tower that can only be described as a relic of a bygone age.
        FITTING_FOR_SOMETHING_HIDDEN_UNDER_THE_SURFACE_THIS                   = 11430,  -- Fitting for something hidden under the surface, this device responded to the earth rune Tellus, which parries lightning strikes as a skilled swordsman deflects his adversary's blade.
        AS_AN_ASIDE_I_TARRIED_WITH_AN_INTERESTING                             = 11431,  -- As an aside, I tarried with an interesting clan of diminutive individuals called Tarutaru before making my way to this dungeon. Despite their slightly annoying speech patterns, they were good folk. They were even kind enough to teach me what they call magic.
        I_WAS_TAKEN_ABACK_BY_THE_SIMILARITY_OF                                = 11432,  -- I was taken aback by the similarity of their magic to Rhazowan geomancers' manipulation of natural forces. I had no idea that elemental sorcery was practiced outside that frozen wasteland to the north.
        JUST_HOW_IS_IT_THEY_CAN_WIELD_SUCH                                    = 11433,  -- Just how is it they can wield such tremendous power with equally prodigious skill?
        TO_TELL_THE_TRUTH_ONE_OF_THE_REASONS                                  = 11434,  -- To tell the truth, one of the reasons I ventured down here was to ascertain the answer to that question. I desperately wanted to find out if these ruins had any connection to the magic the Tarutarus employ.
        ONCE_I_FINISH_MY_INVESTIAGTION_HERE_I_SHALL                           = 11435,  -- Once I finish my investiagtion here, I shall return to their settlement once more and begin anew my inquiry into their wondrous powers.
        THIS_EXPERIENCE_JUST_GOES_TO_SHOW_HOW_LITTLE                          = 11436,  -- This experience just goes to show how little of the world I truly understand... At least I shall not want for discovery and adventure for some time to come.
        ONE_DAY_HOWEVER_I_INTEND_TO_ATTAIN_OMNIPOTENCE                        = 11437,  -- ...One day, however, I intend to attain omnipotence and be the most learned man in Vana'diel! Mark my words, future rune fencer!
